title: ***Open For Tours On Weekends - Newly Renovated - Endless Amenities***
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
